With your permission, I will provide advice on the conduct of this campaign.  If you require my assistance, click the arrows at the top of this message to view additional advice.  If you'll not be needing my advice, close this message window, right-click on my image in the Command Center, and select 'Agent Advice' from the menu. To access this message at a later time, click on the Agent icon in the vertical row currently located to the left of this message. To view other advice messages, click on the 'Message Index' button, the second button from the top on the right.